            <title><![CDATA[Halo On PS5: "We Want To Bring Players Back Together," Microsoft Says About Remake]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gamespot.com/articles/halo-on-ps5-we-want-to-bring-players-back-together-microsoft-says-about-remake/1100-6537490/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f</link>
            <guid>1410745</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><p>
    <span data-nosnippet="">GameSpot may receive revenue from affiliate and advertising partnerships for sharing this content and from purchases through links.</span>
  </p><article itemscope="" data-type-id="1100" data-guid="1100-6537490">

            
            
  


        

  


        
        
              <section>

                  
          <div data-content-element-selector="p, .js-buylink-item-container" data-allowed-classes-selector="js-buylink-item-container">
                <p>For the first time in series history, the Halo franchise will be<a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/halo-is-coming-to-playstation-for-the-first-time/1100-6535696/" data-ref-id="1100-6535696"> playable on PlayStation this year</a> with the release of <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/halo-campaign-evolved-release-date-trailer-news/1100-6535992/" data-ref-id="1100-6535992">Halo: Campaign Evolved</a>. Executive producer Damon Conn said in an interview that Microsoft's goal is to "bring players back together."</p><p>"There are people who have never been exposed to Halo. Maybe they've always been on <a href="https://www.gamesradar.com/tag/sony/" rel="nofollow ">Sony</a> products, switched consoles at a certain point, or just missed it at the time. We want to bring players back together," Conn explained to GamesRadar.</p><p>Creative director Max Szlagor added that, "Halo is best played when we have a large, healthy community."</p><p>Releasing Halo: Campaign Evolved on PS5 is a "way to grow, expand, and reconnect the Halo community," Szlagor said.</p><p>"We want to honor the Halo legacy on PlayStation, and we're paving the way to expand our Halo universe--that's how we see it," Conn added. "And it's not a small thing. We don't and we won't take it lightly. We definitely feel the weight of it."</p><p data-embed-type="video" data-src="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hSjbIM0iegY" data-width="100%" data-height="100%">          <iframe src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/hSjbIM0iegY" height="100%" width="100%" scrolling="no" frameborder="" webkitallowfullscreen="" mozallowfullscreen="" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p>Releasing Halo on PS5 is also a way for Microsoft to make a lot of money potentially. After all, Microsoft has already earned <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/this-xbox-game-just-passed-300-million-in-revenue-on-ps5-report-says/1100-6537323/" data-ref-id="1100-6537323">hundreds of millions of dollars bringing its games to PS5.</a> So far, Forza Horizon 5 has been <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/forza-horizon-5-is-by-far-xboxs-most-successful-port-on-ps5-report/1100-6537371/" data-ref-id="1100-6537371">Microsoft's most commercially successful PS5 port.</a></p><p>Halo: Campaign Evolved is a remake of the 2001 original, but without multiplayer. It's slated for release some time this year on PS5, as well as Xbox and PC, featuring brand-new prequel missions, split-screen co-op, new weapons, visual and audio updates, and more.</p><p>There are other new Halo games in development, and <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/halo-games-will-be-on-playstation-going-forward-says-microsoft/1100-6535712/" data-ref-id="1100-6535712">these titles will come to PlayStation as well.</a> This shift isn't surprising given Xbox president Sarah Bond has said the concept of exclusive games "<a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/exclusive-games-are-antiquated-xbox-president-says/1100-6535625/" data-ref-id="1100-6535625">is antiquated for most people</a>."</p><p>In other Xbox news, the next Xbox Developer Direct is coming up on January 22, <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/xbox-developer-direct-returns-january-22-with-fable-and-forza-horizon-6/1100-6537273/" data-ref-id="1100-6537273">promising news and updates on the new Fable game and Forza Horizon 6, among others. </a></p>
  
                        
    
        
        
  
